{"tid":1638749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Be Humble.］請保持香港人質素，決不淪為大陸人","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:41:34.000Z","uid":312893,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3618aecf959b5e0790947fffefb0affd6fae355c","tid":1638749,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢篇嘢除咗想大家諗清楚裝修一事，亦想大家反思一下自己嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾個例子大家：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家仲記唔記得呢單嘢？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hn7vJuC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHn7vJuC.png&h=4c4e1029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">當初寶礦力抽起TVB廣告，大陸人即刻話要抵制，話寶礦力支持港獨支持暴力。</span></span><br />\n當時嘅連登仔反應是咁的：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soPaJx3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsoPaJx3.png&h=f32e94fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywKNLMo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywKNLMo.png&h=ccc21a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇，到而家，<strong>Vans將3對反送中參賽作品下架，懷疑有政治審查之嫌。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">有人提倡罷買，亦有人提議<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">裝修</span></ins></strong>。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n罷買乃個人選擇，且不作談論。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但若果我哋真係為呢件事而裝修，咪仲衰過班大陸喱？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上只係一個小小例子。無可否認大家心態上係又開始有少少驕傲<br />\n<br />\n當日發夢將軍澳裝修，有個鬼佬行過嚟問我哋點解要幫starbucks、元氣裝修。答咗之後，佢講咗句：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">「所以你哋覺得要破壞哂同你哋立場唔一致嘅店舖？」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一個民主嘅社會係會有唔同聲音。<br />\n人也好、店舖也好。唔係仆街到好似優品或黨鐵咁，大家又何必落人口實呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家，請記得Be Humble。驕兵必敗。</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcPh8po.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcPh8po.png&h=91d0c19b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BA9BEv3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBA9BEv3.png&h=1f23492a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我知自己講到1999，有好多需要學習嘅地方，有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafaa396617f7e6f65310780400448270b451baa","tid":1638749,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19ce090c28fb27fb41b3f13bfaa561bb3609e6ff","tid":1638749,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:00:25.000Z","msg":"入嚟睇吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ba15b125e576cfb3ce8f03820c240006fd674e","tid":1638749,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:00:38.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f35218fbaa474e6bb07f87e9d2b5cf00a44a88d","tid":1638749,"uid":91682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n我地走上呢條頭係因為追求民主自由<br />\n同時我地有一條好清晰對與錯嘅界線<br />\n所以我地先至會屌9藍絲黑白不分<br />\n<br />\nBe water be humble"},{"pid":"de400689247918532614c123d3b3f0dece596dd3","tid":1638749,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f35218fbaa474e6bb07f87e9d2b5cf00a44a88d","tid":1638749,"uid":91682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n我地走上呢條頭係因為追求民主自由<br />\n同時我地有一條好清晰對與錯嘅界線<br />\n所以我地先至會屌9藍絲黑白不分<br />\n<br />\nBe water be humble"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:41:34.000Z","msg":"希望，亦相信我哋能一直堅守呢個信念<br />\n繼續走落去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}